Package: climniche
Type: Package
Title: Niche Relative Climate Exposure
Version: 0.3.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bohao", "He", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bohao.he@polimi.it")
    )
Description: Quantifies projected climate exposure relative to a species'
    current realised climatic niche. Occurrence records, range maps, and binary
    or continuous species distribution model outputs can define the current
    reference. The package reports Climatic Displacement, Niche Distance Shift,
    Climatic Reconfiguration and Niche Boundary Exceedance for single
    projections, ordered time series and climate model ensembles.
